name: R'EVOL #001 - THE OUTLAW (BRIMSTONE VARIANT)
description:
THIS DEVIL IS THE HELLISH VARIANT of "R'EVOL #001 - THE OUTLAW"
 
MUCH MEANER AND MORE DEADLY THAN HIS ORIGINAL, THIS VARIANT LEAVES A TRAIL OF FIRE AND FURY COMING STRAIGHT FROM HELL.

He carries a demonic sword, a mysterious bottle as well as his cowboy hat. He is known for his mask, carrying the classic EVOL design traits.



NOTICE:
While each original R'EVOL character is being minted in editions of 10, a VARIANT will always only exist ONCE and is being sold as a unique 1/1 edition.


Thank you for supporting young and upcoming artists :)
